</style><h3 id="outline__3" class="wp-block-heading">“X日”的挑战</h3><h4 id="outline__3_1" class="wp-block-heading">威克特生产</h4><p>而“以与人才和影响者相同的方式被视为”就就业环境而言意味着同样的事情。</p><p>今年早些时候，WACTOR Productions 雇用拉丁美洲人才的问题曝光。该公司过去曾让多名艺人暂停活动，引起部分观众和粉丝的不信任和不满。）的活动已经达到顶峰。 </p><p></p><figure class="wp-block-embed is-type-wp-embed is-provider-p-2-y-jp wp-block-embed-p-2-y-jp"><div class="wp-block-embed__wrapper"><blockquote class="wp-embedded-content" data-secret="X7VISHgPZ1"> <a href="https://p2y.jp/wactor-production-should-face-the-voices-of-latin-american-listeners-and-fans-in-response-to-the-successive-suspensions-of-affiliated-vtuber/">针对附属VTuber活动的接连停止，WACTOR Productions应该面对的拉丁美洲观众和粉丝的声音</a></blockquote><iframe class="wp-embedded-content" sandbox="allow-scripts" security="restricted" title="“针对附属 VTuber 的活动连续暂停，WACTOR Productions 应该面对拉丁美洲观众和粉丝的声音” — P2y.jp" src="https://p2y.jp/wactor-production-should-face-the-voices-of-latin-american-listeners-and-fans-in-response-to-the-successive-suspensions-of-affiliated-vtuber/embed/#?secret=cDEugcdsQp#?secret=X7VISHgPZ1" data-secret="X7VISHgPZ1" width="600" height="338" frameborder="0" marginwidth="0" marginheight="0" scrolling="no"></iframe></div></figure><figure class="wp-block-embed is-type-wp-embed is-provider-p-2-y-jp wp-block-embed-p-2-y-jp"><div class="wp-block-embed__wrapper"><blockquote class="wp-embedded-content" data-secret="k5jJ4LGykn"> <a href="https://p2y.jp/former-performer-and-voice-model-for-wactor-production-vtuber-hina-misora-and-tsukito-hana-released-a-statement/">WACTOR Production 所属 VTuber Hinami Sora Tsukitohana 前表演者/声优发表声明</a></blockquote><iframe class="wp-embedded-content" sandbox="allow-scripts" security="restricted" title="“WACTOR Productions 旗下 VTuber Hinami Sora Tsukitohana 的前表演者/声优发表声明” — P2y.jp" src="https://p2y.jp/former-performer-and-voice-model-for-wactor-production-vtuber-hina-misora-and-tsukito-hana-released-a-statement/embed/#?secret=9pUe6IxcJg#?secret=k5jJ4LGykn" data-secret="k5jJ4LGykn" width="600" height